  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the therapeutic effect of the infusion of Maytenus ilicifolia
      Mart. ex Reiss leaves, used for 8 weeks, on patients with dyspepsia. Primary endpoint is SODA
      score, secondary endpoint is endoscopic classification (Sydney).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
