  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age &gt; 18 years

          -  being literate

          -  diagnosis of dyspepsia

          -  initial SODA score &gt; or = 25

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnancy

          -  lactation

          -  allergy to Maytenus species

          -  fail to use the drug for 3 uninterrupted weeks

          -  new onset serious adverse events, attributable to the drug

          -  patient's request
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
